                     <list>
                        <item xml:id="a1">
                           <locus target="#143rb">Fol. 143rb</locus>: Ownership note.<q xml:lang="gez">Fol. 143rb: ዝመጽሐፍ፡ ዘቅዱስ፡ ሚካኤል፡ ቤተ፡ ምኳዕ፡ {ድንግለት}፡ ዘአጽሐፎ፡ አቡነ፡ ገብረ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡ [vac.]በሢመቱ፡ [vac.]እ፡ ወጸሐፍያኒሁ፡ ፪አኃው፡ ርእሰ፡ ደብር፡ ኃይለ፡ ኢየሱስ፡ ወመሪ፡ ጌታ፡ አፈ፡ ወርቅ፡ ዘስመ፡ ጥምቀቱ፡ ገብረ፡ ሥላሴ፡ …</q>
                           <q xml:lang="en"/>
                           The note is written in the main hand. It states that the book belongs to the church of Qǝddus Mikaʾel Bet Mukwaʿ Dǝngǝlät and mentions ʾabunä Gäbrä ʾƎgziʾabǝḥer as the commissioner and brothers rǝʾǝsä däbr Ḫaylä ʾIyäsus and märigeta ʾAfä Wärq whose baptismal name is Gäbrä Śǝllase as the scribes.
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="e1">- Erasures marked by thin lines: e.g., fols. 3rb, 31vb, 56ra, 76rb, 78ra.&#xD;
- Corrections written over erasures: e.g., fols. 3ra, 7ra, 10ra, 11va, 17vb, 29va.&#xD;
- Immediate corrections marked by thin lines above and below the words: fol. 34rb. &#xD;
- Omitted letters, words or passages written interlineally or in the margin: e.g., fols. 4vb, 5va, 6rab, 6va, 7ra, 7va.&#xD;
- Compressed script: e.g., fols. 31vb-33rb, 52ra-53va, 57vb-58rb, 67rb-68va.&#xD;
- The word እገሌ is marked above and below by thin lines: e.g., fols. 82vb, 89ra, 142rb.&#xD;
- Spaces for the rubricated names of the donors (and the metropolitan) left unfilled: e.g., fols. 27vb, 44rb, 46ra, 48ra, 48vb.</item>
                     </list>
                  </additions>
